data.title: Eiga-36 - 19 (2019)
data.meta_description: EIGA-36_19 (2019) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is a catalogue of control marks stamped on gas cylinders worldwide. It provides tables listing existing control marks by country in alphabetical order. The marks help identify cylinder characteristics and certification. The publication is maintained by EIGA and includes marks from the original 1990 version as well as Notified Bodies associated with European transport directives. It is intended as a reference for the gases industry.
